### Dependency Injection

An example is worth a thousand words:

```
use DI\Annotations\Inject;

class MyClass {
    /**
     * @Inject
     * @var MyService
     */
    private $service;

    public function doSomething($id) {
        $object = $service->getSomething($id);
    }
}
```

#### Using Zend Framework?

Check out the Zend Framework quickstart with PHP-DI already configured with examples on [zf-quickstart-di](https://github.com/mnapoli/zf-quickstart-di).
